data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This beautiful single-story residence, nestled on an oversized lot, combines elegance with practicality, offering a lifestyle of comfort and luxury.As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious interior featuring 4 well-appointed bedrooms, each designed with your comfort in mind. The master suite is a retreat, providing a sanctuary for relaxation. The Casita, a separate and private space, adds versatility to the property, providing an additional bedroom equipped with its own kitchenette—a perfect haven for guests or extended family members.The heart of the home is the gourmet kitchen, where culinary enthusiasts will appreciate the central island, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The sparkling pool and spa invite you to unwind, and entertain! The paved and gated RV Parking is a standout feature,complete with electric and sewer hookups.Don't miss the opportunity to call this stunning property your home. Schedule a viewing today!
